name: Kim Miller
text: The pizza was amazing...I'm not a big crust eater but even the crust was delicious...$13.00 for a large pepperoni with double mushroom and cheese. Can't beat it!! And the girl on register was very nice.

name: Marvin McFadden
text: I know it's a pizza place and a gas station but it's actually really good. The pizza tastes great. Tasty buttery crust and loaded with toppings and cheese. Definitely recommend.
